name: FISHY STABBER v1.2
description:
See how many fish you can collect before the time runs out.  Combo up for massive bonus points! Match up the fish in the slots quicky to earn more time and points! Simple, fun, addictive!

New in version 1.2 - Dino Reef level! Caution creatures may eat each other! This might ruin your shot, but the more they eat, the bigger they grow. The bigger they grow, the more points they are!
